TS Marco Update

post_text:
Great news! SCI HIGH is a YouthForce NOLA Collaborative Partner High School for the 2020-21 school year! Our school and YouthForce NOLA believe that all of our students have the potential to live happy, prosperous lives -- and we want to connect all of our young people with the career skills, network, and knowledge needed to be successful. YouthForce NOLA is building a pathway for career and life success that we believe all students can utilize to build real-world skills to produce real-life success.
This includes job-specific credentials and soft skills growth, and connecting students with real career experiences that set them up for success, including virtual job site visits and internships.
